<header>

</header>

<section class="main container">
  <label class="title">Frontend Developer & Tester</label>
  <label class="description">I design and code beautifully simple things, and I love what I do.</label>
  <img src="../../svgs/avatar.svg" alt="" class="avatar">
</section>

<img src="../../svgs/devices.svg" alt="" class="devices">

<section class="introduction">
  <div class="container">
    <label class="name">Hi, I’m Manoj. Nice to meet you.</label>
    <p class="description">
      As a frontend developer since 2019, I've worked on diverse projects, collaborated with talented professionals, and
      contributed to exceptional digital products. I continuously refine my skills, embracing new technologies to
      deliver high-quality frontend solutions.
      <LinkTo class="link" @route='about'>Know more</LinkTo>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="experience container">
  <label class="title">WORK EXPERIENCE</label>
  <div class="organisation-container">
    <img src="../../svgs/zoho-logo.svg" alt="" class="logo">
    <div class="details--wrapper">
      <label class="title">Software Developer</label>
      <a href="https://www.zohocorp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="org-name">
        Zoho Corporation
        <svg class="icon svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-up-right-from-square mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"
          data-prefix="fal" data-icon="arrow-up-right-from-square" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 512 512" data-fa-i2svg="">
          <path fill="#FFF"
            d="M336 0c-8.8 0-16 7.2-16 16s7.2 16 16 16H457.4L212.7 276.7c-6.2 6.2-6.2 16.4 0 22.6s16.4 6.2 22.6 0L480 54.6V176c0 8.8 7.2 16 16 16s16-7.2 16-16V16c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16H336zM64 64C28.7 64 0 92.7 0 128V448c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H384c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V304c0-8.8-7.2-16-16-16s-16 7.2-16 16V448c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32H64c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32V128c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32H208c8.8 0 16-7.2 16-16s-7.2-16-16-16H64z">
          </path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="details">
        Extensive expertise in modern frontend technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like EmberJs.
      </p>
      <p class="details">
        Collaborated effectively with cross-functional teams, including designers, backend developers, and product
        managers, to develop a diverse range of products.
      </p>
      <p class="details">
        Managed end-to-end projects independently as a solo frontend developer, overseeing all aspects of development
        and delivery.
      </p>
      <p class="details">
        With proficiency in both manual and automation testing, I have played a pivotal role in ensuring the delivery of
        high-quality software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <label class="title">MY TOOLBOX & THINGS I CAN DO</label>
  <p class="description">The skills, tools and technologies I use to bring your products to life:</p>
  <div class="tools-container">
    {{#each this.toolsList as | tool |}}
    <div class="tool">
      <img src="../../svgs/{{tool.iconName}}" alt="" class="tools-icon">
      <label class="label">{{tool.label}}</label>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="projects container">
  <label class="title">My Recent Work</label>
  <p class="description">Here are a selection of stuff i've built.</p>
  <div class="projects-list">

    {{#each this.projectsList as | project |}}
    <div class="project">
      <img src={{project.imgName}} alt="" class="img">
      <div class="details">
        <label class="title">{{project.title}}</label>
        <label class="description">{{project.description}}</label>
        <a href={{project.knowMoreLink}} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link--wrapper">
          <img src="../../svgs/link.svg" alt="" class="icon">
          Know more
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{/each}}
  </div>
</section>

